modName: tiger retexture and skin addon for sabrecat race
summary: a retexture and nif adjustment to a tiger based on sabrecat
descriptionHtml:
esp and bsa file contain all appropriate files. use bsa browser to extract. 
esp contains a new race and skin/armor addon for the sabrecat . any sabrecat Actor can be made to be reskinned to tiger (not snowy , only regular sabrecat race)

sample provided in cell \"tiger storage\"

enjoy free to use,  to see in action check out my main mod http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9782

please endorse there not the model upload.
free to use, any credits or links to my mainmod appreciated ,but not required.
ooh example actor is non aggresive to player,but is aggresive to mannequins!
author: muppetpuppet
